# Optional: accounts + cross-device sync. Leave unset and Verastar runs fully
# in-browser (IndexedDB) with no account features — the original local-only mode.
# The anon/publishable key is safe to expose in the bundle; row-level security is
# the boundary. Never put a service-role key here.
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
